                    },
                    "body": "I have also ran into this issue when trying to implement a custom error message. Are there any plans to fix this issue, or am I assigning the error message in an incorrect way?\n\n$element = $this->createElement('MultiCheckbox', 'checkbox');\n$element->addErrorMessage('Foo');",
                    "updateAuthor": {
